data.description: This 3 bedroom and 2 bathroom home is in a great location for you and your family! This one level, well maintained and newly painted home has a spacious master bedroom suite that is separated from the other two bedrooms. The open floor plan is perfect for entertaining, and the large fenced in backyard is private and is the best place to enjoy evenings by the fire at your own private patio and firepit area. There is a community pool located close by in this sidewalk community. Come and see it today!
